# Pager
bind pager <Down>   next-line
bind pager <Up>     previous-line
bind pager g        top
bind pager G        bottom
bind pager <Home>   exit

# Index
bind index g        first-entry
bind index G        last-entry
bind index \cR      imap-fetch-mail
bind index N        toggle-new
bind index \cN      mail
bind index r        reply
bind index R        group-reply

